---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Missioni"
  description="Le missioni della Chiesa Efraim: Kenya e India. Scopri come stiamo portando speranza, istruzione e cura spirituale nelle nazioni."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-slate-dark overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-dark/90 to-slate-dark"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-accent rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-primary-light rounded-full blur-3xl translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-28 md:py-36">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-block text-accent font-medium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Raggiungere le nazioni</span>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">
          Le nostre missioni
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          Dal cuore di Messina al cuore del mondo. Crediamo che ogni vita abbia un valore inestimabile e lavoriamo per portare speranza concreta dove ce n'è più bisogno.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Overview -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-warm">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <span class="inline-block text-accent-dark font-medium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">La nostra visione</span>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text mb-6">Portare speranza nel mondo</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-lg">
          La Chiesa Efraim crede nella chiamata di portare il Vangelo e l'amore pratico di Cristo oltre i confini della propria comunità. Attraverso i nostri progetti missionari in Kenya e in India, ci impegniamo a sostenere bambini, famiglie e comunità con programmi di istruzione, nutrizione, acqua pulita e cura spirituale.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Mission Cards -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- Kenya Card -->
        <a href="/missioni/kenya/" class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm border border-divider/50 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="aspect-[16/10] bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mx-auto text-primary/40 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary/60 transition-colors" aria-hidden="true">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                <path d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20" />
                <path d="M2 12h20" />
              </svg>
              <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">Foto della missione in Kenya</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="inline-block w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary-light"></span>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary-dark">Attiva dal 2012</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-text group-hover:text-primary-dark transition-colors">Missione Kenya</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              Kasue, Kitui - Sosteniamo oltre 140 bambini con istruzione, nutrizione e cura spirituale. Un progetto che trasforma vite e dona futuro.
            </p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-dark group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
              Scopri di più
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- India Card -->
        <a href="/missioni/india/" class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm border border-divider/50 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="aspect-[16/10] bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mx-auto text-accent/40 mb-3 group-hover:text-accent/60 transition-colors" aria-hidden="true">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                <path d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20" />
                <path d="M2 12h20" />
              </svg>
              <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">Foto della missione in India</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="inline-block w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-accent-dark">In sviluppo</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-text group-hover:text-primary-dark transition-colors">Missione India</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              Un progetto in crescita per portare istruzione, sostegno e il messaggio del Vangelo alle comunità rurali dell'India.
            </p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-dark group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
              Scopri di più
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Impact Stats -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-primary-dark">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="inline-block text-accent font-medium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Il nostro impatto</span>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">Numeri che raccontano storie</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Years -->
        <div class="text-center p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
          <div class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-accent mb-2">13+</div>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Anni di servizio</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-2">Presenti in Kenya dal 2012</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Children -->
        <div class="text-center p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
          <div class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-accent mb-2">140+</div>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Bambini sostenuti</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-2">Istruzione, nutrizione e cura</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Communities -->
        <div class="text-center p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
          <div class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-accent mb-2">2</div>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Nazioni raggiunte</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-2">Kenya e India</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-cream">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text mb-4">Fai la differenza oggi</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Ogni donazione, grande o piccola, contribuisce a cambiare la vita di un bambino. Unisciti a noi nella missione.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/dona/"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-md hover:bg-primary-dark hover:shadow-lg transition-all"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"/></svg>
        Dona ora
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
